data.description: Beautiful craftsman style home located in NW Redmond. Home offers an open floor plan, two living spaces, kitchen with Island, breakfast bar, SS appliances, granite countertops, hardwood floors, dining area, primary bedroom with walk-in closet, big bathroom suite with soaking tub, open staircase, loft and more. If you like to entertain you will love the backyard! fully landscaped with covered patio and firepit.  This home has been so loved and it's ready for it's new owners! come see it! don't miss out on this adorable home.
